Docs.summary:
Gets the ClientEncryptionKey under an existing Azure Cosmos DB SQL database.
Request Path/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.DocumentDB/databaseAccounts/{accountName}/sqlDatabases/{databaseName}/clientEncryptionKeys/{clientEncryptionKeyName}
Operation IdSqlResources_GetClientEncryptionKey

Gets the ClientEncryptionKey under an existing Azure Cosmos DB SQL database.
Request Path/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.DocumentDB/databaseAccounts/{accountName}/sqlDatabases/{databaseName}/clientEncryptionKeys/{clientEncryptionKeyName}
Operation IdSqlResources_GetClientEncryptionKey

Create or update a ClientEncryptionKey. This API is meant to be invoked via tools such as the Azure Powershell (instead of directly).
